  <summary date="2017-09-25T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Protecting Workers and Improving Labor Standards Act

This bill amends the National Labor Relations Act to allow labor agreements to require membership in a labor organization as a condition of employment regardless of state law (thus preempting state laws that prohibit such agreements).</summary>
